  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Duration of tinnitus &gt; 6 months

          -  Maximum loudness of tinnitus on the VAS ≥ 4

          -  TFI score ≥ 25

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Pregnancy

          -  Psychiatric disorders

          -  Pace maker or defibrillator

          -  Pulsatile tinnitus

          -  Acoustic Neurinoma

          -  CVA
      </textblock>
